def cog_RPM(cogs, n):
    input_check = isinstance(cogs, list) and len(cogs) > 1
    output_check = isinstance(n, int) and n >= 0
    if not (input_check and output_check):
        return None
    RPM = 1
    i = 0
    while i < n:
        RPM = RPM * -1
        i += 1
    RPM2 = 1
    i = 0
    while i < len(cogs) - 1 - n:
        RPM2 = RPM2 * -1
        i += 1
    return [RPM, RPM2]
